ObjectPropertyRange(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000417> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000005>)

# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001927> (specifies value of)

