AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0009006> "A relation between an assay and a characteristic, in which the assay generates a data item which is a measure of a characteristic."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0009006> "assay measures characteristic"@en)
